reviewText: Anastasia dvd starts skipping 15 min into movie and continues. Thumbelina plays just fine, kinda bummed .
My little girl loves watching them over and over. I actually enjoyed the Anastasia version.

I have always loved Thumbelina as a little girl so I was really looking for that DVD... seeing it in a combo with Anastasia was a bonus! I love DVD combos/trios. You really can't beat the value.
